gure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20big%20forces%20at%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20there%20is%20a%20demand%20for%20in-person%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20on-screen%20fatigue%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mike%20Ellery%2C%20chief%20creative%20officer%20at%20Sparks%2C%20which%20has%20worked%20with%20Netflix%20on%20in-person%20activations%20like%20its%202024%20Emmy%20season%20event.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20want%20to%20do%20things%20that%20are%20live.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESales%20for%20live%20events%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-investors-vc-live-events-entertainment-rebound-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econcerts%20and%20sporting%20events%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20bounced%20back%20to%20(or%20even%20exceeded)%20pre-pandemic%20levels%2C%20with%20communal%20experience%20a%20big%20part%20of%20the%20draw%2C%20according%20to%20Deloitte.%20Surveys%20by%20MG2%20Advisory%2C%20a%20retail%20design%20and%20architecture%20firm%2C%20have%20shown%20that%20Gen%20Z%20has%20become%20more%20interested%20in%20in-person%20interactions%20and%20pop-up%20experiences%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20after%20being%20relegated%20to%20screens%20during%20the%20pandemic%20lockdown.%20Two%20of%20five%20of%20these%20adults%2C%2018%20to%2026%2C%20shopped%20mostly%20or%20entirely%20in-store%20in%202025%2C%20MG2%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20there's%20the%20desire%20from%20media%20companies%20for%20new%20ways%20to%20grow%20revenue.%20Netflix's%20frenzied%20days%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-earnings-preview-wall-street-password-sharing-ad-tier-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esubscriber%20expansion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20are%20over%2C%20and%20the%20time%20people%20are%20spending%20watching%20its%20shows%20and%20movies%20is%20slowing.%20MrBeast%2C%20for%20his%20part%2C%20is%20racing%20to%20become%20profitable%20as%20his%20company%20eyes%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-beast-industries-business-profit-strategy-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epotential%20IPO%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20looks%20to%20deliver%20for%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20want%20to%20wring%20more%20value%20out%20of%20the%20massive%20amount%20of%20money%20they%20spend%20on%20content%2C%20and%20one%20way%20to%20do%20that%20is%20by%20getting%20fans%20to%20engage%20more%20deeply%20with%20them%20in%20areas%20like%20in-person%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20acknowledgment%20that%20the%20battle%20for%20time%20is%20sort%20of%20a%20fool's%20errand%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20media%20analyst%20Doug%20Shapiro%2C%20a%20senior%20advisor%20at%20BCG.%20%26quot%3BTime%20is%20finite.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226189%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20Netflix%20House%20outside%20Philadelphia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691f0c5fabd5e944effb1c27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224081%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFans%20of%20%26quot%3BWednesday%26quot%3B%20can%20step%20inside%20Nevermore%20Academy%20at%20Netflix%20House.%3Cp%3Ekat%20kendon%2FKat%20Kendon%20%2F%20NETFLIX%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e6110c77-8cbe-438f-a3a1-83f9560a2d98%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENetflix%20and%20MrBeast%20want%20to%20let%20fans%20experience%20their%20brands%20in%20real%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20initial%20experiments%20by%20Netflix%20and%20MrBeast%20are%20moderately%20priced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Netflix%20games%20cost%20%2425%20to%20%2440%20a%20pop%20to%20play%2C%20while%20Beast%20Land%20charges%20%247%20to%20enter%20and%20up%20to%20%2466%20for%20all-access%20to%20the%20rides.%20That's%20roughly%20on%20par%20with%20attractions%20like%20the%20Top%20of%20the%20Rock%20observation%20deck%20at%20New%20York%20City's%20Rockefeller%20Center%20(starting%20at%20%2442)%2C%20but%20cheaper%20than%20a%20major%20theme%20park%20like%20Disney%20World%2C%20which%20starts%20around%20%24120%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20slate%20of%20Netflix%20Houses%20will%20be%20located%20in%20malls%2C%20allowing%20people%20to%20easily%20return%20to%20them.%20The%20experience%20is%20varied%20enough%20within%20each%20locale%2C%20and%20from%20city%20to%20city%2C%20that%20you%20could%20see%20people%20coming%20back%20with%20friends%2C%20as%20a%20couple%2C%20or%20with%20kids%20to%20do%20different%20things%20each%20time%2C%20said%20Melissa%20Gonzalez%2C%20founder%20and%20principal%20of%20MG2%2C%20which%20has%20developed%20escape%20rooms%20and%20immersive%20pop-ups%20for%20brands%20like%20Victoria's%20Secret%20(Netflix%20isn't%20a%20client).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20uses%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Gonzalez%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20way%20they%20designed%20this%2C%20things%20are%20naturally%20Instagrammable.%20It%20feeds%20into%20the%20experience%20economy.%20The%20younger%20generation%20wants%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MrBeast%20team%20modeled%20its%20Beast%20Land%20attractions%20after%20its%20videos%2C%20with%20one%20game%20featuring%20the%20%26quot%3Btrap%20doors%26quot%3B%20gimmick%20that%20has%20become%20a%20signature%20in%20MrBeast%20competitions.%20The%20goal%20was%20to%20allow%20fans%20to%20experience%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20compete%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-prime-renews-mrbeasts-beast-games-for-more-seasons-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMrBeast%20challenge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20YouTuber%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELetting%20people%20walk%20through%20a%20space%20or%20participate%20in%20a%20challenge%20they've%20seen%20on%20screen%20brings%20instant%20emotional%20connection%20and%20loyalty%2C%20Ellery%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Scene%20from%20Netflix%20House%20near%20Philadelphia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e43a8abd5e944effb1678%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENetflix%20House%20wants%20attendees%20to%20leave%20with%20a%20souvenir.%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229f8f2893-c3e7-4a22-a3f8-febf26d0610a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20business%20case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20not%20to%20consider%20these%20new%20ventures%20without%20thinking%20of%20Disney%2C%20which%20has%20built%20a%20%2436%20billion%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-house-disney-world-theme-parks-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparks%20and%20experiences%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20off%20its%20famous%20characters%20and%20stories.%20The%20MrBeast%20team%20has%20even%20pitched%20investors%20on%20plans%20to%20build%20out%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-building-next-disney-ceo-pitching-beast-industries-to-investors-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDisney-style%20empire%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20initial%20efforts%20from%20Netflix%20and%20MrBeast%20don't%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-parks-economy-recession-disney-world-disneyland-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDisney-scale%20ambitions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20has%20said%20it's%20not%20making%20its%20%26quot%3BHouses%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20money%20but%20to%20connect%20more%20deeply%20with%20fans.%20Netflix%20has%20also%20historically%20moved%20slowly%20into%20new%20areas%2C%20committing%20in%20a%20way%20that%20doesn't%20spook%20investors%20(see%3A%20its%20foray%20into%20video%20games).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProjects%20like%20Netflix's%20and%20MrBeast's%20have%20a%20natural%20cap%20on%20scale%20compared%20to%20larger%20theme%20parks%2C%20which%20rely%20on%20massive%20numbers%20of%20visitors%20who%20come%20for%20longer%20and%20spend%20a%20lot%2C%20said%20Jason%20Ambler%2C%20chief%20content%20officer%20of%20Falcon's%20Beyond%2C%20which%20develops%20and%20operates%20entertainment%20destinations%20and%20whose%20clients%20have%20included%20Disney%20and%20Universal%20Studios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20smaller%20formats%20are%20more%20agile%20and%20replicable%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20companies%2C%20the%20real%20value%20isn't%20in%20the%20business%20itself%20but%20in%20how%20these%20experiences%20boost%20the%20brand%20and%20drive%20sales%20elsewhere%2C%20Ambler%20said.%20Branded%2C%20in-person%20experiences%20let%20companies%20quickly%20and%20safely%20test%20new%20ideas%2C%20stay%20visible%20between%20product%20releases%2C%20and%20strengthen%20connections%20with%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeast%20Land%20has%20a%20partner%20in%20Riyadh%20Season%2C%20a%20Saudi%20entertainment%20festival%2C%20and%20is%20running%20for%20a%20limited%20time%2C%20which%20reduces%20MrBeast's%20financial%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20capital%20outlay%20may%20be%20relatively%20small%20for%20Netflix%20and%20MrBeast%2C%20launching%20these%20experiences%20isn't%20risk-free%2C%20Gonzalez%20said.%20Netflix's%20shows%20have%20to%20translate%20into%20a%20real-world%20environment%20and%20not%20feel%20shallow%20or%20gimmicky.%20There%20may%20be%20licensing%20complexities.%20Replicating%20the%20approach%20in%20different%20locales%20with%20different%20footprints%20can%20take%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20experiments%20aren't%20going%20to%20turn%20into%20a%20billion-dollar%20business%20overnight%2C%20Netflix%20and%20MrBeast%20may%20consider%20them%20a%20success%20if%20they%20determine%20%E2%80%94%20through%20tracking%20things%20like%20customer%20satisfaction%20and%20spending%20over%20time%20%E2%80%94%20that%20they%20keep%20fans%20watching%2C%20subscribing%2C%20and%20buying%20other%20things%20the%20company%20sells.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarketing%20is%20another%20goal.%20These%20experiences%20are%20designed%20for%20attendees%20to%20take%20selfies%20and%20post%20them%2C%20helping%20spread%20the%20word%20to%20a%20wider%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20creating%20this%20shareable%20experience%20that%20you%20can%20have%20in%20real%20life%20with%20your%20friends%20and%20your%20people%2C%20and%20you%20can%20amplify%20that%20with%20social%20really%20easily%2C%26quot%3B%20Ellery%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20rule%20out%20the%20possibility%20that%20these%20experiences%20could%20grow%20into%20something%20bigger%20down%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20successful%20franchises%20start%20to%20think%20about%20how%20they%20can%20further%20monetize%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Scott%20Purdy%2C%20a%20media%20industry%20consultant%20at%20KPMG%20US.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20going%20down%20a%20path%20others%20have%20in%20terms%20of%20business%20maturity.%20When%20companies%20slow%20down%20from%20frenzied%20growth%2C%20you%20start%20to%20look%20at%20other%20avenues.%20Can%20it%20be%20a%20real%20business%3F%20Yes.%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20just%20a%20marketing%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-mrbeast-test-theme-parks-irl-experiences-boost-engagement-growth-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763648391000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691f1dc4abd5e944effb1d38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-mrbeast-test-theme-parks-irl-experiences-boost-engagement-growth-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Netflix's%20and%20MrBeast's%20theme%20parks%20offer%20immersive%20experiences%2C%20meeting%20demand%20for%20interactive%20and%20IRL%20entertainment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmoses%40insider.com%20(Lucia%20Moses%2CDan%20Whateley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-mrbeast-test-theme-parks-irl-experiences-boost-engagement-growth-2025-1