nteractive%20Advertising%20Bureau.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20up%2026%25%20year-over-year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vertical%20is%20growing%20four%20times%20as%20fast%20as%20the%20overall%20media%20industry%2C%20per%20IAB's%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20context%2C%20the%20largest%20digital%20ad%20segment%20tracked%20by%20the%20IAB%20last%20year%20was%20search%2C%20at%20%24102.9%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%202025%20spending%20estimate%20on%20creators%20is%20nearly%20triple%20the%20amount%20from%202021%2C%20when%20social-media%20consumption%20was%20booming%20amid%20the%20pandemic%20lockdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20things%20driving%20the%20spike%20in%20interest%20in%20creators%20among%20brands%2C%20said%20Zoe%20Soon%2C%20an%20IAB%20VP%20who%20focuses%20on%20emerging%20advertising%20channels%20like%20the%20creator%20economy%20and%20gaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20influencers%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bbuilt-in%20distribution%26quot%3B%20network%20to%20serve%20ads%20across%20social%20channels.%20Second%2C%20they%20have%20proven%20cultural%20relevance%20among%20young%20people.%20And%20third%2C%20they%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20connect%20with%20%26quot%3Bad-avoidant%26quot%3B%20Gen%20Z%20consumers%20at%20a%20time%20when%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bdiminishing%20places%20that%20you%20can%20reach%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Soon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreators%20are%20now%20considered%20more%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bmust-buy%26quot%3B%20than%20other%20emerging%20ad%20categories%20like%20connected%20TV%20and%20commerce%20media%20among%20the%20roughly%20450%20US%20ad%20spending%20decision-makers%20who%20responded%20to%20the%20IAB's%20survey%20between%20July%20and%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIAB%20earlier%20projected%20connected%20TV%20ad%20spending%20would%20hit%20%2426.6%20billion%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCreator%20content%20is%20outperforming%20brand-led%20content%20across%20almost%20all%20metrics%2C%26quot%3B%20Dontae%20Mears%2C%20an%20SVP%20of%20influencer%20marketing%20at%20Weber%20Shandwick%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20three%20key%20takeaways%20from%20IAB's%20report%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222219e008-39f0-452b-b273-91980690a111%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20The%20creator%20ads%20business%20is%20eating%20up%20spending%20from%20legacy%20channels%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20was%20tough%20to%20get%20a%20brand%20advertiser%20to%20put%20more%20than%20an%20experimental%20budget%20behind%20influencer%20campaigns.%20That's%20not%20true%20today.%20Marketers%20know%20they%20have%20to%20invest%20in%20creator%20content%20if%20they%20want%20to%20reach%20some%20audiences%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20harder%20to%20scale%20than%20a%20campaign%20run%20on%20Facebook%20or%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20legacy%20formats%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcable-tv-household-50-percent-decline-brian-wieser-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elinear%20TV%20lose%20audience%3C%2Fa%3E%20share%20each%20year%2C%20marketers%20have%20to%20adapt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20creators%20are%20%26quot%3Bdriving%20the%20cultural%20zeitgeist%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20you%20have%20other%20channels%20that%20advertisers%20are%20not%20seeing%20as%20effective%20anymore%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20makes%20sense%20that%20they%20start%20moving%20those%20dollars%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chris%20Bruderle%2C%20IAB's%20VP%20of%20industry%20insights%20and%20content%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22588074e5-6efe-4bf3-a15e-b59080dc0746%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Mid-tier%20creators%20reign%20supreme%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMid-tier%20influencers%20with%20between%2050%2C000%20and%20500%2C000%20followers%20were%20the%20most%20commonly%20hired%20by%20respondents%20to%20IAB's%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESixty-one%20percent%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20hired%20mid-tier%20influencers%2C%20followed%20by%2055%25%20who%20said%20they%20worked%20with%20eit