a%20bullish%20view%20on%20the%20two%20stocks%20for%20the%20last%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20after%20turning%20over%20every%20stone%2C%20we%20no%20longer%20see%20a%20credible%20path%20back%20to%20cloud%201.0%20economics.%20The%20market%2C%20however%2C%20still%20prices%20in%20that%20outcome%2C%20implying%20returns%20we%20believe%20are%20no%20longer%20achievable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20key%20differences%20between%20the%20business%20model%20for%20%26quot%3Bcloud%201.0%26quot%3B%20and%20generative%20AI%2C%20Haissl%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20one%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20AI%20is%20far%20more%20costly.%20According%20to%20Rothchild's%20analysis%2C%20a%20GPU%20costs%20firms%20around%20%2440%20billion%20in%20capex%20per%20gigawatt%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20believed%20to%20generate%20less%20revenue.%20Each%20GPU%20generates%20around%20%2410%20billion%20of%20revenue%20per%20gigawatt%2C%20per%20the%20firm's%20calculations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221434%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chart%20showing%20revenue%20and%20capex%20estimates%20for%20GenAI%20hardwar%20and%20traditional%20cloud%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e028589026fbb4d0df64a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22885%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERothschild%20%26amp%3B%20Co%20Redburn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Meta%2C%20Alphabet%2C%20and%20Apple%20are%20on%20track%20to%20spend%20around%20%24349%20billion%20in%20capex%20this%20year%2C%20much%20of%20which%20is%20directed%20toward%20AI%20infrastructure%2C%20according%20to%20company%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20concerned%20about%20operating%20margins%3B%20those%20can%20be%20managed.%20The%20real%20constraint%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-capex-spending-ai-earnings-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecap